Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.939 --> 00:00:03.060
My name is Paul Sandberg.

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:06.000
I'm an actor, singer, and teacher in the New
York City area.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.070
For more information, please visit my website
